it.cnr.isti.thematrix.scripting.aggregate.support

Class Min

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.cnr.isti.thematrix.scripting.aggregate.support.AggregateFunction
      • it.cnr.isti.thematrix.scripting.aggregate.support.Min

  • public class Min
extends AggregateFunction
    Min implements the minimum AggregateFunction, defined on INT, FLOAT, DATE and BOOLEAN types only. Exploits the comparable interface of the object in the accumulator. Null values are ignored after issuing a warning in the logs. TODO Value casting is currently unsupported. May need an int to float cast in the float version. May need proper casting in the case of boolean arguments.
    Author:
    edoardovacchi
